eNCA's Moloko Moloto reports. #DStv403 LIMPOPO - Victims of a multiple-vehicle crash in Limpopo have been laid to rest. 16 people were killed on the R579 near Motetema in Groblersdal. READ: 19 dead in Limpopo accidents The taxi was allegedly attempting to overtake when it collided head-on with the truck. A second taxi was also damaged in the crash. 